John de Jongh, Jr.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from John de Jongh)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with John de Jong.


John Percy de Jongh Jr.








7th Governor of the United States Virgin Islands


In office
January 1, 2007 – January 5, 2015


Lieutenant
Gregory Francis


Preceded by
Charles W. Turnbull


Succeeded by
Kenneth Mapp





Personal details


Born
John Percy de Jongh, Jr.
(1957-11-13) November 13, 1957 (age 59)
Brooklyn, New York


Political party
Democratic


Spouse(s)
Cecile René Galiber


Children
